### Are you looking for diabetes information in languages other than English?
We’ve translated some of our key patient information and education resources
They’re packed with tips on everything from diet to treatment and prevention.
You can also order printed copies of some publications in foreign languages
Did you know you can watch our ‘What is diabetes?’ video with Bengali,
Gujarati, Hindi, Polish, Punjabi or Urdu subtitles? Just click the ‘subtitles’
button on the video below to turn them on.
